634
01:49:41,049 --> 01:49:43,718
Neka vas sami nađu.

635
01:51:45,882 --> 01:51:48,076
Detektive Vilijamse!

636
01:51:48,176 --> 01:51:52,080
Detektive Vilijamse! -Ovde
Vilijams. To si ti, Džefri?

